---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PAYMENTS | ACHI Studio" description="Available payment methods and transaction security details.">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-charcoal">PAYMENTS</h1>
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-400 mt-2 font-light">Supported Payment Options</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm font-light text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        To ensure a premium shopping experience, ACHI supports several secure payment options for all orders.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-base uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium mt-8 mb-4">Credit & Debit Cards</h3>
      <p>
        We accept Visa, Mastercard, and JCB cards. All transactions are securely encrypted using standard SSL connections.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-base uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium mt-8 mb-4">Bank Transfer & QR Payment</h3>
      <p>
        You can make a direct bank transfer or use Thai QR Payment (PromptPay) during the checkout process. PromptPay QR codes are generated instantly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
